     C           KEYF81    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           DAHTYY
     C                     KFLD           DAHTMM
     C                     KFLD           DAHTDD
      *
     C           KEYCB1    KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KBMN   40
     C                     KFLD           #KHN1   5
     C                     KFLD           #KHN2   5
     C                     KFLD           #KHN3   2
      *
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KBMN
     C                     KFLD           #KKDAI  1
      *
     C           KEY2      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           #KBMN
     C                     KFLD           #KKDAI
